name: Michigan football
summary: Michigan football pulled off an upset 13-10 victory over No. 2 Ohio State on Saturday, marking the first win by an unranked Michigan team against a ranked Buckeyes squad in over two decades. The victory boosted Michigan's momentum ahead of the Big Ten Championship Game, where they will face Purdue. The game was marred by a post-game scuffle, and analysts predict that Michigan has a strong chance of repeating their upset victory in the championship game. Several top recruits also visited Ann Arbor for the game against Northwestern.

name: Barcelona
summary: On November 30, 2024, Barcelona suffered a surprising 2-1 loss to Las Palmas, marking their first home defeat of the season. ESPN provided an in-depth analysis of the game. The club also announced the indefinite closure of a portion of their stadium, with The Athletic investigating the reasons behind this decision. Ahead of their UEFA Champions League match against Stade Brestois, Forbes and Sports Illustrated released predicted lineups for Barcelona, with coach Flick making some changes. Barcelona secured a 3-0 victory against Brest in the match, described as a "stronghold blaugrana" by the club's official media. CNET reported on the availability of livestreams for the upcoming Barcelona vs. Las Palmas La Liga match. The Associated Press highlighted Barcelona's loss, while ESPN and The Athletic commemorated the club's 125th anniversary with articles on key moments and historical milestones. Finally, Forbes reported on an incident involving a Barcelona player who vomited blood and was stretchered off after a nasty blow during a match.

However, their upset over BYU caused significant upheaval in the rankings. The Big 12 conference issued a public reprimand and fine to Arizona State, casting a shadow over their recent successes. As they prepare for the upcoming Territorial Cup matchup, experts predict a competitive showdown between the Sun Devils and Wildcats.
